    <title>EXPRESS: Cross-Platform Spillover Effect of Promotion: Evidence from the PC Game Market</title>
    <updated>2026-01-22T00:00:00+00:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Seongkyoon Jeong, Sanghoon Cho, Moonwon Chung</name>
